{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.160", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.200", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.200", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erwerbsarbeit sorgt nicht nur f\u00fcr Einkommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.200", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern bedeutet mehr f\u00fcr die Menschen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gesellschaftliche Teilhabe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.360", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "soziale Kontakte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.640", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "W\u00fcrde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.200", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anerkennung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.600", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wertsch\u00e4tzung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb darf ein Sozialstaat niemanden alleinlassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.280", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "niemanden vergessen und auch niemanden aufgeben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.440", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alle Menschen brauchen Chancen und Perspektiven."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.760", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Realit\u00e4t sieht aber anders aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.040", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Besch\u00e4ftigtenquote ist hoch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und doch hat sich die Langzeitarbeitslosenzahl verfestigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.560", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Menschen aber dauerhaft vom Arbeitsmarkt ausgeschlossen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.160", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann hat das Folgen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.280", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das macht auch etwas mit den Menschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.280", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie werden immer mehr an den Rand der Gesellschaft gedr\u00e4ngt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.360", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und viele empfinden das auch so. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.400", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darauf geben die bisherigen arbeitsmarktpolitischen Instrumente keine Antwort. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.080", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das muss sich \u00e4ndern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.360", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es muss Schluss sein mit kurzfristigen Programmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Unterscheidung zwischen erstem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.120", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zweitem und gar drittem Arbeitsmarkt ist nicht die L\u00f6sung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.760", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Notwendig ist endlich ein Perspektivwechsel hin zu einem Arbeitsmarkt f\u00fcr alle. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.160", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau dar\u00fcber haben wir auch bei den Jamaika-Sondierungen verhandelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.160", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und jetzt steht es im Koalitionsvertrag von Union und SPD. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.000", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber viele Fragen bleiben offen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.840", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Idee vom sozialen Arbeitsmarkt funktioniert jedoch nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.800", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn auch tats\u00e4chlich die Rahmenbedingungen stimmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.560", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb geben wir Ihnen mit unserem heute vorliegenden Antrag die Anforderungen an einen sozialen Arbeitsmarkt mit auf den Weg."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.240", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die gef\u00f6rderte Besch\u00e4ftigung muss zu den Menschen passen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.720", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihren Interessen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.200", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00e4higkeiten und auch St\u00e4rken entsprechen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.920", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb muss das freiwillig sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.040", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zwang und Sanktionen darf es nicht geben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.041", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.041", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.760", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Koalitionsvertrag steht zu Recht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.560", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der soziale Arbeitsmarkt gemeinn\u00fctzigen und auch gewerblichen Betrieben offensteht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.280", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es fehlt jedoch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.920", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die bisherigen Kriterien \u201ezus\u00e4tzlich\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.880", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eim \u00f6ffentlichen Interesse\u201c und \u201ewettbewerbsneutral\u201c entfallen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist aber zentral und wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.000", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit sich wirklich alle Betriebe an der sozialen Integration von langzeitarbeitslosen Menschen beteiligen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.040", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier m\u00fcssen Sie unbedingt nachbessern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.800", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.040", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist ganz wichtig\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.240", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit der Arbeitsmarkt tats\u00e4chlich f\u00fcr alle offensteht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss die gef\u00f6rderte Besch\u00e4ftigung zu einem dauerhaften Angebot werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.520", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das geht nur mit einem Passiv-Aktiv-Transfer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.960", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.400", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die passiven Leistungen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.520", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Arbeitslosengeld\u00a0II und die Kosten der Unterkunft\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.480", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden in einen Lohnkostenzuschuss umgewandelt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.000", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn nur so wird statt Arbeitslosigkeit tats\u00e4chlich Erwerbsarbeit finanziert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.800", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber genau das steht nicht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumindest nicht klar\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.640", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Koalitionsvertrag."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.200", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da steht nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.200", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Eingliederungstitel j\u00e4hrlich um 1\u00a0Milliarde Euro aufgestockt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.880", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist aber gerade einmal die Summe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.520", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die den Jobcentern fehlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.960", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil der Verwaltungshaushalt chronisch unterfinanziert ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.760", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich kann nur sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.600", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ein sozialer Arbeitsmarkt ohne einen konsequenten Passiv-Aktiv-Transfer kommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.600", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ist das nichts anderes als eine riesengro\u00dfe Mogelpackung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.320", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das w\u00e4re nicht akzeptabel."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.000", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jahrelange und verfestigte Arbeitslosigkeit darf es nicht geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.960", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb wollen wir Gr\u00fcnen eine solidarische Arbeitsmarktpolitik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.120", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen Arbeitsmarkt f\u00fcr alle. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.400", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur das entspricht einer inklusiven Gesellschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.200", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nicht mehr ausschlie\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.480", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern die W\u00fcrde der Menschen in den Mittelpunkt stellt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.040", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und genau daran werden wir Sie messen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.440", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.160", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.000", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.000", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als N\u00e4chstes erteile ich dem Kollegen Kai Whittaker von der CDU/CSU-Fraktion das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}